@startuml seq-inference-sync
title Синхронный инференс — Enterprise ML Platform (Baseline/Alpha)

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 5
skinparam sequenceParticipant underline

actor "Клиент\n(Приложение)" as Client
participant "WAF\n(AWS WAF)" as WAF
participant "ALB\n(AWS ALB)" as ALB
participant "API Gateway\n(Kong/Envoy)" as GW
participant "Redis\n(auth cache)" as RedisAuth
participant "Inference Service\n(Triton)" as Inf
participant "Redis\n(prediction cache)" as RedisCache
participant "GPU / Triton\n(GPU Pool)" as GPU
participant "Kafka\n(inference-logs)" as Kafka

Client -> WAF : POST /v1/infer\nHTTPS, API-Key header
note right of WAF
  OWASP ruleset: проверка на
  SQL injection, XSS, payload size.
  Блокировка при совпадении правил.
end note

WAF -> ALB : Filtered HTTP request

ALB -> GW : HTTPS → HTTP\nPath-based routing: /v1/infer

== Аутентификация и Rate Limiting ==

GW -> RedisAuth : GET api_key:{sha256(key)}
RedisAuth --> GW : tenant_id + permissions (cache hit ≤1ms)

alt API key не найден / истёк
    GW --> Client : 401 Unauthorized
end

GW -> RedisAuth : INCR rate_limit:{tenant_id}:{minute}\nEXPIRE 60s
RedisAuth --> GW : current_count

alt Превышен лимит (Token Bucket)
    GW --> Client : 429 Too Many Requests\nRetry-After: 60s
end

note right of GW
  Rate limit: 1000 req/min per tenant_id
  (Token Bucket, configurable per plan)
end note

== Инференс ==

GW -> Inf : gRPC InferenceService.Predict(request)\nrequest_id, tenant_id, model_id, inputs

Inf -> RedisCache : GET prediction:{model_id}:{hash(inputs)}

alt Cache Hit
    RedisCache --> Inf : CachedPrediction (TTL 5 мин)
    note right of Inf
      Cache hit: пропуск GPU вызова.
      ~85% hit rate для однотипных входных данных.
    end note
else Cache Miss
    RedisCache --> Inf : nil

    alt Circuit Breaker OPEN (GPU деградация)
        note right of Inf
          Состояние Open: error rate >50% за 10s
          или 3 подряд timeout >5s.
          Пауза 30s, затем Half-Open.
        end note
        Inf --> GW : gRPC UNAVAILABLE\n"GPU pool unavailable, retry in 30s"
        GW --> Client : 503 Service Unavailable\nRetry-After: 30s
    else Circuit Breaker CLOSED / HALF-OPEN
        Inf -> GPU : Triton gRPC ModelInferRequest\n(model_name, inputs, outputs)
        GPU --> Inf : ModelInferResponse\n(outputs, model_version)

        Inf -> RedisCache : SET prediction:{model_id}:{hash(inputs)} {result}\nEX 300 (TTL 5 мин)
        RedisCache --> Inf : OK
    end
end

Inf -> Kafka : produce InferenceLogged\n{request_id, tenant_id, model_id,\nlatency_ms, cache_hit, timestamp}
note right of Kafka
  Fire-and-forget: async produce.
  Не блокирует ответ клиенту.
  Topic: inference-logs
end note

Inf --> GW : gRPC OK\n{prediction, model_version, latency_ms}
GW --> Client : 200 OK\n{prediction, model_id, version, request_id}

note over Client, Kafka
  SLA: p99 ≤100ms (NFR-101).
  Critical path: WAF→ALB→GW→Inf→GPU≈60-80ms.
  Cache hit path: WAF→ALB→GW→Inf→Redis≈15-25ms.
end note

@enduml